-- S.Africa's Abil lacks "bandwidth" for overhaul -acting CEO
-- By David Dolan
-- Wed Aug 06, 2014 10:35AM EDT
-- None



JOHANNESBURG, Aug 6 (Reuters) - South Africa's African Bank Investments <ABLJ.J> does not have enough "bandwidth" within its executive team to deal with the necessary restructuring on its own, the bank's acting chief executive said on Wednesday.

